memberdef.initializer: { \ icUInt32Number nv=(N); \ size_t ss = os.pStack->size(); \ if (nv>ss) \ return false; \ icFloatNumber *sv = &(*os.pStack)[ss-nv]; \ memcpy((X), sv, nv*sizeof(icFloatNumber)); \ os.pStack->resize(ss-nv); \ }

memberdef.name: OsPushArgs
memberdef.initializer: { \ size_t ss = os.pStack->size(); \ icUInt32Number nv=(N); \ os.pStack->resize(ss+nv); \ icFloatNumber *sv = &(*os.pStack)[ss]; \ memcpy(sv, (X), nv*sizeof(icFloatNumber)); \ }
